txt.en: Talk to Damrod in Barad Orhant
Damrod can be found in Barad Orhant in Minas Morgul.\n\nYou should talk to Damrod.
Shades and fell spirits can be found in the Circle of Sorrow in Minas Morgul.\n\nYou should defeat any shades and fell spirits that you find.
'You have done the Rangers of Ithilien a great service, but there is still more to be done if we are to cleanse the shadow from this corrupted city.'

'We must lessen the numbers of fell spirits who wander upon the Circle of Sorrow. I ask you to defeat any of the spirits and shades that you see as you venture out into Minas Morgul. Beware, for they are treacherous and will seek to do you harm!'
Damrod wishes to defeat the many shades and spirits that haunt the Circle of Sorrow in Minas Morgul.
